{"tid":616025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班交警涉危駕被捕　稱撕警遊樂會泊車證為取證","createTime":"2018-04-04T00:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T01:56:26.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"39f9b451a8357b68a103f98f7b0ef42a35979279","tid":616025,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1330155/org/29fe19a96a3a3360f66a6024887f3664.jpg/bwtXOgkOaFqM5LfM5DBYboSNOtDBae1vG9bfyBvW38g?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1330155%2Forg%2F29fe19a96a3a3360f66a6024887f3664.jpg%2FbwtXOgkOaFqM5LfM5DBYboSNOtDBae1vG9bfyBvW38g%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=faac2e60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日下午大埔公路沙田嶺段發生的奪命車禍，一名鐵騎士駕駛電單車駛至大埔公路近大埔道眺望處時，被對面行車線一輛失控的私家車撞倒，電單車司機頭部重傷，送院後不治。<br />\n\t<br />\n據了解，肇事私家車司機為一名27歲休班警員，駐守新界南交通總部。新界北交通部特別意外隊第一隊何泰然督察指，事發時，肇事私家車由大埔公路沙田嶺段往沙田方向行駛，駛至近大埔道眺望處時，突然失控，越過雙白車撞向對面線的電單車，電單車再撞向路邊交通標誌，司機頭部重創，送往醫院搶救後不治。私家車司機涉危險駕駛導致他人死亡被捕，惟他頭部受傷仍需留院觀察，但獲准保釋，他須於5月中向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，現時循三個方向調查，分別是私家車及電單車事發時的車速、車輛的機件性能，以及兩位司機的精神狀態，特別是私家車司機。警方指仍在事發現場找尋行車記錄器（車Cam），警方呼籲目擊者向警方提供資訊，案件由新界東北交通部跟進。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，事發時，有現場人士見到私家車檔風玻璃上貼有警察體育遊樂會泊車證，惟警員到場調查時將肇事私家車車頭的行車證，及警察體育遊樂會泊車證除去。記者問及為何要取走相關物件時，何泰然指，警方於現場取證物時，可取走任何一樣認為與案有關的物件。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1330157/org/cad0abeaea0bddc27f5f671995a7b258.png/LeRGOSHaVLZg8q1fK2U7Y5wRV1ZZ_fDy_REeJP0RHiQ?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1330157%2Forg%2Fcad0abeaea0bddc27f5f671995a7b258.png%2FLeRGOSHaVLZg8q1fK2U7Y5wRV1ZZ_fDy_REeJP0RHiQ%3Fv%3Dw640&h=4ae1fb02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1330156/org/41474ea64a312f7906921bc9b9699707.jpg/pciIxJmXI_UPr9YBi_hQgx4X6Jl7HfpTkSeOYJEnjmA?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1330156%2Forg%2F41474ea64a312f7906921bc9b9699707.jpg%2FpciIxJmXI_UPr9YBi_hQgx4X6Jl7HfpTkSeOYJEnjmA%3Fv%3Dw640&h=4ea237f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據悉，電單車司機姓林，與妻子及一對子女住在大圍美城苑。鄰居指，林一家人在上址住了十多年，一對子女就讀中學，妻子有工作。鄰居又指，平日出入大家會打招呼，知道他任職救生員。林平日有踩單車，但不知道對方有電單車。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，死者家屬到醫院認屍，眾人神情凝重，傷心不已，更數度流淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1330159/org/be1b991a17c8f6ce86e43546ab2eb69c.jpg/ryNQCZcxaMQ55mjIGTQkEBCijuuNCSeIe_7tlnv-7ZY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1330159%2Forg%2Fbe1b991a17c8f6ce86e43546ab2eb69c.jpg%2FryNQCZcxaMQ55mjIGTQkEBCijuuNCSeIe_7tlnv-7ZY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=d9585989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撰文：彭愷欣楊婉婷王譯揚<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/174625/%E5%A5%AA%E5%91%BD%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E4%BA%A4%E8%AD%A6%E6%B6%89%E5%8D%B1%E9%A7%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E7%A8%B1%E6%92%95%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83%E6%B3%8A%E8%BB%8A%E8%AD%89%E7%82%BA%E5%8F%96%E8%AD%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F174625%2F%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25A6%258D-%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%25A7%2595%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%2592%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B3%258A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%258F%2596%25E8%25AD%2589&d=fMMf8xppSEyiJECW3yj3UjANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=9478c065\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/174625/%E5%A5%AA%E5%91%BD%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E4%BA%A4%E8%AD%A6%E6%B6%89%E5%8D%B1%E9%A7%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E7%A8%B1%E6%92%95%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83%E6%B3%8A%E8%BB%8A%E8%AD%89%E7%82%BA%E5%8F%96%E8%AD%89</a>"},{"pid":"90798913b6bb18f2e865899e7179f65e6322dd43","tid":616025,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:03:45.000Z","msg":"賊匪所為<i